NAME
    Catalyst::Plugin::Flavour - Catalyst plugin for request flavours.

SYNOPSIS
        use Catalyst qw/Flavour/;

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin allows you to handle request flavours like Blosxom.

EXTENDED METHODS
  prepare_path
SEE ALSO
    Catalyst

    http://www.blosxom.com/

